<plot>Pupperty and songs are the make-up of this "Musical Parade" featurette (production number FF6-4), featuring Roger Dann, Sally Rawlinson and Bob Baker's Puppets. Dann is in love with Sally, daughter of the puppeteer, but is thwarted because he is not a success. (This Bob Baker definitely not the same as the Universal western star of the late 1930's.)</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423893</url></doc>
